      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey im type 1 diabetic and i just finished a long run but now im feeling really weird. i feel super shaky and sweaty and kinda lightheaded like im in a fog. i think maybe my sugar is too high because of the stress of the workout? should i take a bit of extra insulin to bring it down so i feel normal again?",
